    {
      "id": "6c676d44-2790-4e1b-bfb4-f8c7a1103d1d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Work focuses on identifying cheating behaviors in online courses. It treats cheater detection as a combination of anomaly detection AND supervised ML. Authors create behavioral features using literature and try to find anomalies. Results show that classifiers trained on data of cheating behabviors becomes effective at identifying cheating behaviors across different types of cheating and acrooss different courses.",
